Outside the gym, attendees line up before the event opens as career center staff log attendance metrics on laptops and distribute lanyards. Concurrently, an alumni panel discusses preparation strategies for technical interviews. Various employers, including consulting firms showcasing glossy case study booklets and a robotics startup flying a small drone, attract attention, along with healthcare providers showcasing community outreach photos. Workshops on networking etiquette commence in an adjoining classroom, complemented by a cybersecurity company conducting a password cracking challenge on a laptop. As the event wraps up, volunteers tidy up by stacking collapsed booths and collecting leftover brochures, while career counselors remind attendees to maintain eye contact during presentations. A post-event survey link flashes on the monitors near the exit.

Inside, the atmosphere is busy with an alumni panel discussing strategies for technical interview preparation, while career counselors assist students at a resume review table near the stage, focusing on elevator pitches and maintaining eye contact. Students use tablets at kiosks to upload resumes to the fair database. Workshops on networking etiquette occur in an adjoining classroom, with coffee and catered snacks available nearby. A cybersecurity company conducts a password-cracking challenge on laptops, while a robotics startup gains attention by flying a small drone above its booth. As the event concludes, announcement chimes signal the final hour, and volunteers stack collapsed booths, gathering leftover brochures.

Alumni panelists discuss strategies for technical interview preparation, alongside workshops on networking etiquette and a resume review table in an adjoining classroom. Consulting firms showcase glossy case study booklets, and healthcare providers display community outreach photos. A robotics startup attracts attention with a small drone flying above its booth, and a data science company features a live dashboard of fair attendance. The aroma of coffee and catered snacks fills the lounge, and as some students rehearse elevator pitches quietly against the wall, interview sign-up sheets begin to fill, accompanied by announcement chimes. Volunteers tidy up and remind attendees to take advantage of lingering opportunities.
